                </dd>
            </dl>
            <dl class="stat">
                <dt class="stat__title delta">Developer List</dt>  
                <dd class="stat__value">
                    Get answers to questions and find out what is next for glimpse on our <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/?fromgroups#!forum/getglimpse-dev" target="_blank">community user group</a>
                </dd>
            </dl>
            <dl class="stat">
                <dt class="stat__title delta">Twitter</dt>  
                <dd class="stat__value">
                    Feel free to get in touch with the us on twitter using either <a href="http://www.twitter.com/anthony_vdh" target="_blank">@@anthony_vdh</a> or <a href="http://www.twitter.com/nikmd23" target="_blank">@@nikmd23</a>
                </dd>
            </dl>
